'''Nicole Fantl''' is the actress who played [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Lexi Dio/Legends|Lexi Dio]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] (2002).

Before appearing in ''Attack of the Clones'', she appeared in a 2000 episode of ''Water Rats,'' as well as the films ''Alone Together'' (1998, Eric Eason), ''Moulin Rouge!'' (2001, Baz Luhrmann, featuring [[Ewan McGregor]]) and ''Queen of the Damned'' (2002, Michael Rymer). Fantl was also the English voice of Fran in the 2006 game ''Final Fantasy XII''.

